00:15:25,795 --> 00:15:28,695
Which is what I think
he wanted you to believe.

133
00:15:29,285 --> 00:15:32,285
I've talked to him
about the adoption too, and...

134
00:15:33,975 --> 00:15:36,975
The way he sees it,
Bess and you were fighting...

135
00:15:37,795 --> 00:15:40,345
too much, and you gave
his brother away.

136
00:15:41,626 --> 00:15:44,690
And things are so difficult
for him right now that...

137
00:15:44,815 --> 00:15:48,215
