151
00:16:34,305 --> 00:16:36,455
That's quite a lot to live up to.

152
00:16:36,825 --> 00:16:38,175
You'd think that.

153
00:16:39,875 --> 00:16:41,540
The year I was in the seventh grade,

154
00:16:41,665 --> 00:16:45,065
he started taking long drives
on the weekends by himself.

155
00:16:46,005 --> 00:16:48,860
My brother and I got on our bikes
and we rode around the neighborhood,

156
00:16:48,985 --> 00:16:50,485
looking for his car.

157
00:16:51,535 --> 00:16:54,335
And we found it in the driveway
of this little house.

158
00:16:56,485 --> 00:16:58,285
My brother made me ring the buzzer.

159
00:16:58,865 --> 00:17:02,065
The door opened,
and there was my father's secretary,

160
00:17:03,455 --> 00:17:05,438
